          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
            You work hard and deserve to enjoy your weekends, not spend them cleaning. That's where we come in. Whether you need weekly maintenance to stay ahead of busy family life, or a thorough deep clean before hosting guests, The Valley Clean Team understands what Hampton Cove homeowners expect - and we deliver every time.
          </p>
