            <Icon name="briefcase" class="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">Work-Schedule Friendly</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We get it - you're both working, kids have activities, and weekends are precious. We'll clean while you're at the office. Provide a key or garage code, and we'll lock up securely when done. Come home to a pristine house and actually have time to enjoy your Hampton Cove lifestyle.</p>
        </div>

