          <p class="text-gray-600">Dogs? Cats? Kids? No problem. Many Hampton Cove homes have all three. We use family-safe, pet-friendly products and we're comfortable working around your furry friends. Our team members are parents and pet owners too - we understand family dynamics and work around them seamlessly.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-200 service-card">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985] to-[#FFC67D] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="home" class="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">Open Floor Plan Experts</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Hampton Cove homes feature those beautiful open-concept great rooms - kitchen flowing into dining and living areas. We're experienced cleaning these modern layouts efficiently while respecting your furniture arrangement and decor. High ceilings? Ceiling fans? We bring tall ladders and attention to detail.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-200 service-card">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985] to-[#FFC67D] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="bolt" class="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
