          <p class="text-gray-600">Last-minute guests? Post-party cleanup? Need help before showing your home? We offer same-day service when you're in a pinch. Just call before noon and we'll do our best to fit you in. Life happens fast - your cleaning service should keep up.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-200 service-card">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985] to-[#FFC67D] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
