          <p class="text-gray-600">Military discipline meets Southern hospitality. We're punctual, detail-oriented, and treat your home with respect. Licensed, bonded, and insured with background-checked team members. The same values that served our country now serve Hampton Cove families.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Popular Services -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#333333]">
