          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Our most popular service for Hampton Cove families. Weekly or bi-weekly cleaning keeps your home consistently pristine. Same team, same day, same excellence. Stop spending weekends cleaning and start living your life.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
