            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start text-sm text-gray-700">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>Dusting, vacuuming, mopping throughout</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start text-sm text-gray-700">
